title: dance-trance synth sounds - Emulator X/X2 ban
description:
Samplerbanks.com - dance-trance synth sounds - Emulator X/X2 soundbank

Great sample package, a set of multi-sampled and categorized instrument of the famous Clavia Nord Modular G2 synthesizer, collected into the E-MU Emulator X/X2 soundbank, using all the great features of this sampler. 

Shaking basses, dark pads and swirling arpeggios, cutting-edge leads are all there to add a distinctive character, to make your mind blowing and your production shine.

Realtime control possibilites are also added: just move the modulation wheel to change several parameters in real-time in order to make sound breathe.
